step_data.thought: I'm now on the Customers page and can see a list of customers. I need to find Jane Doe with the email jane.doe@example.com and delete her account. Looking at the table, I can see three Jane Doe entries, and I can identify the one with email jane.doe@example.com in row 1908. This is the account I need to delete. To delete this account, I first need to select it by checking the checkbox next to her name. The checkbox is in cell 1909 with ID 1911.
